reviewText: My son has watched this and I have to admit...the adults of the household were spellbound to see what happened next.

I love this season. I think it's the best of the series; it all leads to a satisfying finale, and Master Chen is both plenty evil and plenty funny! Season 5 has already aired in it's entirety, and I thought that season was good as well, it just seemed like a small step down from this one. All in all, highly recommended to anyone and everyone!

Much better than Season 3!!  I think my ten year old and eight year old were just about to give up on Ninjago but this Season really got more interesting with each episode.  My husband and I are hooked, too.  There are 10 episodes between two discs.

Disc 1:
The Invitation
Only one can remain
Versus
Ninja Roll
Spy for a spy

Disc 2:
Spellbound
The Forgotten Element
Day of the Dragon
The Greatest Fear of All
The Corridor of Elders
